metadata.description:
"Colorful Vandalism" is a generative art project inspired by the spirit of street art and graffiti.
Each of 64 iteration is a unique creation, never to be replicated.
Each generative output has the attributes of rarity, so you can find very rare pieces in this collection.

2000 x 3000
Made with p5.js
metadata.name: Colorful Vandalism #1
